'''Sagebrush''' was a type of [[Grass/Legends|grass]] native to [[Praesitlyn/Legends|Praesitlyn]]. It had a strong scent, and many were [[Allergy/Legends|allergic]] to it.

During her tenure as [[Administrator/Legends|administrator]] at the [[Intergalactic Communications Center]] on Praesitlyn, [[Reija Momen]] reflected humorously that, despite its allergenic properties, sagebrush and other native grasses could engender good health in those exposed to it for protracted periods of time.<ref name="JT">''[[Jedi Trial]]''</ref>

